---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — PhoneHub"
  description="PhoneHub affiliate disclosure. Learn how we earn commissions from partner links at no extra cost to you."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-accent-blue/10 border border-accent-blue/20">
        <p class="text-accent-blue font-medium">
          <strong>FTC Disclosure:</strong> PhoneHub may earn commissions from affiliate links on this site at no additional cost to you. This helps support our work and keep the platform free.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
        <p>
          PhoneHub contains links to products on retailer websites such as <strong class="text-gray-200">Amazon</strong>, <strong class="text-gray-200">Flipkart</strong>, and other partner platforms. These links contain special tracking identifiers that let the retailer know you came from PhoneHub. When you click on one of these links and subsequently make a purchase, we may receive a small commission from the retailer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Does This Affect You?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-white">No.</strong> The price you pay for any product through our affiliate links is exactly the same as if you had visited the retailer directly. You will never pay more because you clicked a link on PhoneHub. The commission comes out of the retailer's marketing budget, not from your pocket.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Does This Influence Our Content?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-white">No.</strong> Our editorial content, product reviews, ratings, and recommendations are not influenced by affiliate relationships. We do not favor products because they have higher affiliate commissions. Our product listings are based on specifications, features, and objective analysis. Affiliate revenue helps us maintain and improve PhoneHub, but it does not determine which products we feature or how we review them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Our Affiliate Partners</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">PhoneHub currently participates in the following affiliate programs:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Amazon Associates</strong> — We earn a commission on qualifying purchases made through Amazon links.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Flipkart Affiliate</strong> — We earn a commission on qualifying purchases made through Flipkart links.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Other Partners</strong> — We may participate in additional affiliate programs from time to time. All affiliate links are clearly identifiable by their URL structure.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">How to Identify Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          Affiliate links on PhoneHub typically contain tracking parameters in their URLs (such as <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-navy-700/60 text-xs text-accent-blue">?tag=</code> or <code class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-navy-700/60 text-xs text-accent-blue">?aff=</code>). Product links and "Check Price" buttons throughout the site may be affiliate links.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your Support</h2>
        <p>
          Using affiliate links on PhoneHub is one of the best ways to support the platform at no cost to yourself. The commissions we earn help us maintain the site, aggregate product data, and continue providing free comparison tools and reviews. We appreciate your support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Questions?</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure, please visit our <a href="/phonehub/contact" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
